Feel the pulse-pounding intensity as the top 16 teams converge on the battleground for a shot at ultimate glory in BGIS history. This is more than just a tournament round, it's the climax of the BATTLEGROUNDS MOBILE INDIA SERIES 2024, where dreams soar and legends are made. With a massive prize pool of INR 2 Crores, the stakes are at their peak.

snippet.title: Indian Family and Foreigner  | Take A Break x @BhaDiPa
snippet.description:
Brace yourself for a comedy spectacle in our latest sketch, "Indian Family and Foreigner"! 😂🏡
In this side-splitting episode, we delve into the chaos that ensues when an Indian family plays host to a special guest – a Canadian colleague of the family's father. What starts as a simple visit quickly spirals into an uproarious whirlwind of cultural misunderstandings, hospitality overload, and neighborhood mayhem.
#LaughOutLoud #YouTubeSketch

It was a nice experience of working with Paula McGlynn from @BhaDiPa if you like this collab please let us know in comments.😇🙌

snippet.title: Meet the new member of our Family
snippet.description:
Hello friends, I am back from my break and will start posting new recipes next week. But before that I wanted to share some happy news with you. Thank you all for your wonderful comments and your warm wishes. 

For the upcoming weeks, if you have some recipe suggestions please leave a comment with the recipe name and I will try to make those recipes.

 घना उत्त मिलग्या,

बदनाम ना करे,

बदनाम ना करे,

मैंने घना उत्त मिलग्या,

snippet.title: Sipahi  - Amit Bhadana - Official Full Movie
snippet.description:
Rate Sipahi on IMDB - https://www.imdb.com/title/tt32765621/

This special film showcases the struggle of Sanatan Vijay, a poor boy aspiring to join the police force as a constable. Dedicated to the hardworking youth of the nation who dare to dream, 'Sipahi' aims to uncover their struggle and inspire everyone. Through Sanatan Vijay's story, the film celebrates resilience and determination, making it a poignant tribute to those who strive to overcome their circumstances and achieve their dreams.

Episode 4124: Popatlal Ki Kundli
--------------------------------------------------------
Popatlal grows increasingly anxious while waiting for Inspector Pandey's call to find out if his horoscope matches with the potential bride's. With each passing moment, his impatience mounts. How will Popatlal cope with the suspense and uncertainty surrounding his future?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:
Calcium is a crucial mineral for healthy bones. And when we think of calcium, we think of milk. But you will be surprised that there are 5 foods that have more calcium than milk. 

Try Mamaearth's Nourishing Tinted Lip Balm - https://mamaearth.oia.link/g27gp
(Apply code FITTUBER21 to get 21% off)
Buy from Amazon - https://amzn.to/45LlDL1
(Disclaimer - This is a promotion of the product and not the brand. I assure that this product is 100% toxin free and can be used to get rid of chapped lips and give a pinkish tone to the lips.)

00:00 - Why is calcium so important?
02:12 - Why does our body get deficient in calcium?
03:20 - #5 Food that has more calcium than milk - According to Ayurveda, this is the best source of calcium. You can safely get it from a paan shop nearby.
04:51 - #4 Food that has more calcium than milk - This is a time tested supplement to increase calcium in the body.
06:31 - #3 Food that has more calcium than milk. This lentil has the maximum calcium.

09:33 - #1 Food that has more calcium than milk. This is a surprise when it comes to calcium rich foods.

snippet.title: Arvind Akela Kallu, Shilpi Raj –  गरम मसाला (Video) | Garam Masala | VYRL Bhojpuri
snippet.description:
अरविन्द अकेला कल्लू और शिल्पी राज का नवका गाना गरम मसाला।

Listen to Garam Masala on:

Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/track/5Q4ImfY0s2KXtOA72OFpMn?si=5da2724f3142495f
Wynk: https://wynk.in/u/GX1X1stQe
Apple Music: https://music.apple.com/us/album/garam-masala-single/1751905823
JioSaavn: https://www.jiosaavn.com/song/garam-masala/OQM9dQBHcWQ

Make your reels: https://www.instagram.com/reels/audio/1185421966141654/

#VYRLBhojpuri #ArvindAkelaKallu #ShilpiRaj


Singers: Arvind Akela Kallu, Shilpi Raj
Lyrics: Bhagirath Pathak
Music: Vicky Vox

Ft. Pratishtha Thakur

Director/Choreographer: Aslam Khan
DOP: Shiv Shakti/Rahul Yadav
Editor Santokhs Khera 
Post Production Mad Fx Studioz
Asst.Choreographer: Naveen Thakur 

Project Managed By: Shivay Film's
Project Design By: Abhay Pandey 
Special Thanks: Amit Singh 
Concept Vijay: Chauhan

Music release inquiries: contact.vyrlregional@umusic.com 

Lyrics:
Love kare khatir babu ginjan kartar 
Love kare khatir babu ginjan kartar 
Kahe bol siz apan injan kartar
Panche mint me ho jaib tu pala ka deb halla 
Tohar mixy hamar mixy duno ke mixy ba kala kala 
Hamar pise naram masala tohar pise garam masala
Hamar pise naram masala tohar pise garam masala

Sandile ke mar lage khojtar
Hali me khali naw bojhtar
Hali me khali
Mot jani chhod mal patar kara
Bhale du char din aatar kara 
Hamar bura apan kail chah bhala bantar lalla
Tohar mixy hamar mixy duno ke mixy ba kala kala 
Hamar pise naram masala tohar pise garam masala

Aage se hamra ke gher tar
Bharal bajar me tu chhed tar
Fail ka da aaj gori halua 
Pis pis kallua ke aluaa ke 
Ae bhagirath aat ab na sahala mar deb bhala
Tohar mixy hamar mixy duno ke mixy ba kala kala 
Hamar pise naram masala tohar pise garam masala
Hamar pise naram masala tohar pise garam masala

----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: कुरकुरी भिन्डी - इसे चाय के साथ खायें या सब्जी की तरह चावल-रोटी-परांठे के साथ | Crispy Bhindi Recipe
snippet.description:
कुरकुरी भिन्डी, जो सब्जी भी है और स्नैक्स भी, और बनने में समय भी बहुत कम लगे. तो फटाफट बना डालिये,  crispy okra fry,  kurkuri bhindi masala fry, 
#bhindi #snacks #sabji #teatime 

Ingredients for Kurkuri Bhindi
भिंडी - Ladyfinger - 250 grams
नमक - Salt - 1/2 tsp
हल्दी पाउडर - Turmeric powder - 1/4 tsp
धनिया पाउडर - Coriander powder - 1 tsp
लाल मिर्च - Red chilli - 1/2 tsp
गरम मसाला - Garam masala - 1/2 tsp
चाट मसाला - Chat masala - 1 tsp
चावल का आटा - Rice flour - 4 tbsp
बेसन - Gram flour - 2 tbsp
नमक - Salt - 1/4 tsp
कश्मीरी लाल मिर्च - Kashmiri red chilli - 1/2 tsp

Subscribe for more recipes - 
http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=nishamadhulika

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to SONY AATH Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBz9qbqujcjIavFmBJW2oZw?sub_confirmation=1

Gopal ventures into farming and producing vegetables. But will Maharaj be okay with his venture?

Show Name: Gopal Bhar - গোপাল ভর
Directed By: Sourav Mondal, Hansa Mondal
Written By: Hansa Mondal
Original language:  Bengali
Episode No: 1062

#GopalBhar #sonyaath #গোপালভর 

About Gopal Bhar:
-----------------------------
Gopal Bhar was a legendary court jester in medieval Bengal. He was in the court of Raja Krishnachandra, the famous king of Nadia in the 18th century AD. Such was the genius of Gopal that the King considered him as a Navaratna of his court. His statue can still be seen in the palace of Raja Krishnachandra. Stories about his exploits are narrated in Bengal to this day and are immortalized in countless short stories. The stories are short, beautiful, humorous and have a specific social message. Gopal Bhar is famous for stories of his wisdom, in which he outwits other fellow courtiers.

snippet.title: KUCHI ICE | FRUIT POPSICLES | Healthy Homemade Colorful Popsicle Making in Village | Stick Ice Cream
snippet.description:
Today, in our village, we make colorful, healthy fruit Popsicles, which are 90s kids' favorite snakes of our childhood. We call these popsicles Kuchi Ice or Stick Ice. We use some healthy fruits, such as Mango, Pomegranate, Grape, and Kiwi, for this ice cream. We use a silicon Popsicle Mold, which is used for making ice Popsicles at home. Finally, we taste this Ice in the summer evening!

Yummy!

About MaaTri Media 

MaaTri, represents the most beautiful relationship between a mother and a daughter - Nisha Topwal & Anantya Anand aka. MyMissAnand. MaaTri is formed through a combination of two Hindi words - Maa (Mother) and PuTri (daughter) that brings forth energy, enthusiasm and determination to spread positive vibes through their outstanding content. Their content revolves around fashion, food, comedy, parenting, travel, glimpse of their family and simple day-to-day activities that both enjoy doing together.

Episode 4122: Tension Mein Popatlal
--------------------------------------------------------
After a frantic search, Popatlal is finally discovered locked in his closet. When asked about his disappearance, he opens up about the overwhelming stress and tension that had been building up inside him. Will the colony members offer him support and relief?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4122 | 27 June 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Coke Studio Bharat | Leta Jaijo Re | Shashwat Sachdev x Sunidhi Chauhan x Chotu Khan
snippet.description:
The legacy of Rajasthani culture echoes its history from its palatial havelis, speaks of furtive & shy romances through its stone walls and sings folk songs of tradition & meticulous courtship, cherished and passed down through generations. 
‘Leta Jaijo Re’ is sung like a love song but experienced as a celebration. The song celebrates the beginning of a young couple’s love story, through the willingness to give away a token of your love. 
Acclaimed music super producer Shashwat Sachdev strings together this piece of cultural story-telling through his global yet rooted pallette weaving beautifully Sunidhi Chauhan’s contemporary prowess. 

*CREDITS*

localized.title: Coke Studio Bharat | Leta Jaijo Re | Shashwat Sachdev x Sunidhi Chauhan x Chotu Khan
localized.description:
The legacy of Rajasthani culture echoes its history from its palatial havelis, speaks of furtive & shy romances through its stone walls and sings folk songs of tradition & meticulous courtship, cherished and passed down through generations. 
‘Leta Jaijo Re’ is sung like a love song but experienced as a celebration. The song celebrates the beginning of a young couple’s love story, through the willingness to give away a token of your love. 
Acclaimed music super producer Shashwat Sachdev strings together this piece of cultural story-telling through his global yet rooted pallette weaving beautifully Sunidhi Chauhan’s contemporary prowess.
